sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/GitOps
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as RHODS Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster Controller
    participant GatewayCtrl as Gateway Controller
    participant IngressCtrl as OpenShift Ingress Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controllers
    participant Registry as Container Registries<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 1: Component Enablement (DataScienceCluster Creation)

    User->>API: kubectl apply DSC CR<br/>Auth: kubectl token
    API->>Webhook: Validate DSC<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS1.2+<br/>Webhook cert
    Webhook->>API: Validation response
    API->>DSCCtrl: Watch event: DSC created
    DSCCtrl->>API: Create Component CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    DSCCtrl->>CompCtrl: Reconcile components
    CompCtrl->>API: Create Deployments, Services<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    CompCtrl->>Registry: Pull images<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Pull secret
    Registry-->>CompCtrl: Container images
    CompCtrl-->>API: Component deployed

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 2: Gateway Deployment (Platform Ingress Setup)

    DSCCtrl->>GatewayCtrl: Initialize gateway
    GatewayCtrl->>API: Create GatewayClass<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    GatewayCtrl->>API: Create Gateway (openshift-ingress ns)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    GatewayCtrl->>IngressCtrl: Provision gateway endpoint<br/>via Kubernetes API
    IngressCtrl-->>GatewayCtrl: Gateway ready
    GatewayCtrl->>API: Create EnvoyFilter (ext_authz)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    GatewayCtrl->>API: Create kube-auth-proxy Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    GatewayCtrl->>API: Create OAuthClient<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 3: External User Request (RHOAI 3.x with Authentication)

    participant ExtUser as External User
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Gateway as Gateway<br/>data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant EnvoyFilter as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuthSvc as OpenShift OAuth/OIDC<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Backend as Backend Service<br/>via HTTPRoute
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant AppContainer as Application Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    ExtUser->>Router: HTTPS request<br/>443/TCP TLS1.3
    Router->>Gateway: Route to gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Gateway->>EnvoyFilter: ext_authz check
    EnvoyFilter->>AuthProxy: Validate session<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.3
    alt No valid session
        AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: 401 Unauthorized
        EnvoyFilter-->>ExtUser: Redirect to login
        ExtUser->>OAuthSvc: OAuth/OIDC login<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Client credentials
        OAuthSvc-->>ExtUser: OAuth code/OIDC tokens
        ExtUser->>AuthProxy: Callback with code<br/>via oauth-callback-route
        AuthProxy-->>ExtUser: Set session cookie<br/>httpOnly, secure
    end
    alt Valid session
        AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: 200 OK (authorized)
        EnvoyFilter->>Backend: Forward request via HTTPRoute<br/>OAuth/OIDC headers
        Backend->>RBACProxy: Request to workload<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.3<br/>Bearer token
        RBACProxy->>API: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
        API-->>RBACProxy: RBAC decision
        RBACProxy->>AppContainer: Proxy to app<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
        AppContainer-->>RBACProxy: Response
        RBACProxy-->>Backend: Response
        Backend-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Router: Response
        Router-->>ExtUser: HTTPS response
    end

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 4: Monitoring and Metrics

    participant PromRHOAI as Prometheus (RHOAI)<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant CompMetrics as Component ServiceMonitors
    participant ClusterMon as OpenShift Cluster Monitoring<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Alertmanager as Alertmanager<br/>9093/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3

    PromRHOAI->>DSCCtrl: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (no auth)
    PromRHOAI->>CompMetrics: Scrape component metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer token/mTLS
    PromRHOAI->>ClusterMon: Federate metrics<br/>HTTPS/9091 TLS1.3<br/>Bearer token
    PromRHOAI->>Alertmanager: Fire alerts<br/>HTTPS/9093 TLS1.3
    Alertmanager->>OAuthSvc: Send notifications<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Webhook secrets
